1780418196944158	edict-dev	itc:v3:AWLkkmTOfzk5kQAAAAAAQeqtbv7rtAAAAAEv2AE		item.create	bn-nyr2	{"description":"After maw bare->root migration + edict sync, AGENTS.md managed section updates (content-diff staleness) but .agents/edict/*.md do not (version hash is template-source-only), leaving inconsistent docs. Include layout in compute_docs_version so a layout flip invalidates .version and re-renders workflow docs. Touches sync.rs (compute_docs_version, check_docs_staleness + call site) and init.rs (free sync_workflow_docs hash), plus a test.","kind":"bug","title":"Fold layout into docs-version hash so layout migration re-renders workflow docs"}	blake3:uuwuZexDuBmKhkFPybbNCNAgtraj70GBH6aVTtSBbFk
